If this is present, complete mode deployment will not delete the resource if it is removed from the template since it is managed by another resource.

    ContainerServiceOSDisk:

      type: object
      properties:
        count:
          type: integer
          format: int32
          enum:
            - 1
            - 3
            - 5
          x-ms-enum:

            modelAsString: false
